name: Perturbed Party Planner
content:
Perturbed Party Planner was a Lanai residing on Ahch-To. They were a party planner and had set up much music and games, however, no one was dancing. As a result, the Practical Party Planner asked a Protocol droid to help get five Lanai to dance and start the party.
"Perturbed Party Planner" first appeared in a puzzle titled "Lanai Luau" in the 2022 non-canonical video game LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga.
